{"tid":1858711,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"內地手機出貨　首季勢跌三成","createTime":"2020-02-03T01:08:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T09:19:56.000Z","uid":271829,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"37e872ac0493a5cbd2ee9ca907ab789f0603d627","tid":1858711,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T01:08:43.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】武漢肺炎疫情令蘋果公司的內地廠房局部停工，連帶拖累相關手機股。研究機構Strategy Analytics調查指出，全球70%的智能手機都是由內地生產，人力不足問題顯現，估計內地手機出貨量於首季下滑30%，比預期衰退5%；全球出貨量也將同步減少2%，建議半導體製造商、內容供應商等，密切留意庫存過多的風險。<br />\n<br />\n新iPhone受衝擊較小<br />\n此外，廣發證券執行董事暨海外電子產業首席分析師蒲得宇指出，內地品牌手機庫存調整將拉長，特別是華為和OPPO等庫存調整問題；有鑒於換手機動力放緩，故下調華為、OPPO、vivo以及小米等首季出貨量預測，分別按季減18%、19%、32%、19%，降至4,600萬部、2,500萬部、2,100萬部以及2,600萬部。<br />\n<br />\n由於蘋果今年採取上下半年均有新產品的策略，上半年新產品、尺寸較小的iPhone SE2出貨會否受到衝擊，蒲得宇指整體而言，iPhone受到的影響相較Android陣營的手機少，而iPhone SE2早已啟動量產，今年首季出貨500萬部。蒲得宇分析[日，假設2月是疫情高峯期，科技股有望因需求延遲在首季底反彈。<br />\n<br />\n內地手機出貨 首季勢跌三成<br />\n <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20200203&amp;sec_id=15307&amp;s=0&amp;a=20855411\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200203%26sec_id%3D15307%26s%3D0%26a%3D20855411&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7V5Mi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=a66d8704\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200203%26sec_id%3D15307%26s%3D0%26a%3D20855411&h=f067f9a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20200203&amp;sec_id=15307&amp;s=0&amp;a=20855411</a>"},{"pid":"fe63cac8d0cf6732a6da10ef625d4c7a3bc63cf2","tid":1858711,"uid":3171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T01:09:31.000Z","msg":"美孚手足比人打到出腦漿<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1858244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1858244</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不可忘記黑警暴行"},{"pid":"1288995360b2707d906b45c9de726e128be0a539","tid":1858711,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T01:15:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a4f9c6a8d0f572b1a2476e884da18c7892a327","tid":1858711,"uid":7206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T01:19:59.000Z","msg":"好多潛在用家死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee136ce4063215c30ac69a1f173f2704952d60c","tid":1858711,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T01:35:26.000Z","msg":"屎為收皮"},{"pid":"f7148e2e0def4279e0959337eba8105d3e7992e3","tid":1858711,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T09:00:56.000Z","msg":"經過呢穫走資更加多 連中國商家佬都走埋一份"},{"pid":"80878522354f90bd328a517b5939f2fdc6914bf2","tid":1858711,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T09:19:56.000Z","msg":"仲唔趁機停產等幾時<br />\n反正多數都係賣唔出擺倉底咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}